# Summary
This documentation page describes Amplitude Data's Facebook Ads integration, which imports campaign-level metrics (impressions, clicks, spend) as Daily Ad Metrics events. The integration requires a Facebook Ads Account ID, imports data daily for the previous day, and relies on UTM parameters for proper attribution and calculating metrics like CAC and ROAS.

